{"id":"e17b9d0eb0f80b2e2c448cb6bc10674b7469784691fbf17a41d1c9e91de280bb","item_id":"092e9e8256:0","text":"要在 RenderMan for Blender 中为几何体渲染置换，请使用"}
{"id":"022543dbe3b58a1681fca19925453b701d7a289d04c90ad0f56ea226c7858d89","item_id":"092e9e8256:1","text":"PxrDisplace"}
{"id":"741c40f3e15b45be5bc053e437463ae8b6a01b386d234c46f5e4e6761ccea238","item_id":"092e9e8256:3","text":"添加 PxrDisplace"}
{"id":"75669d96e5847ae7f76b2db41633f8a2a1aa105ccc086fecbf95c1a76764cfc0","item_id":"092e9e8256:4","text":"要添加 PxrDisplace，请确认已经为几何体添加了 RenderMan 材质。在材质属性"}
{"id":"d8a628d5bb4c95fbe0d16ee6333db4d9c33382744be392354ee76fd3b31748f6","item_id":"092e9e8256:5","text":"中，在 Displacement（置换）面板下，从 \"Displacement\" 旁边的下拉列表中选择 PxrDisplace。"}
{"id":"a97fb5009de6ccb8418c31bb827e8a98e6d7915e0bd7e33379840e8c97dd85aa","item_id":"092e9e8256:6","text":"你可能主要会使用以下参数："}
{"id":"29dff695886d9a57875d39f80b823b2e03909130c4d9d69b6895f2b8692d58ef","item_id":"092e9e8256:9","text":"置换的 Gain。若为零，则不会产生置换。"}
{"id":"7eeb26199b5df3b2048150e2427560d7e8c78c708fb3e1724d51c4fa9263f110","item_id":"092e9e8256:12","text":"Scalar Displacement（标量置换）输入。这是一个 float 置换（浮点置换）。"}
{"id":"358fb5400bf7a034f189e8098d5a798e2882bd243cfb42fde29482ff119d1853","item_id":"092e9e8256:15","text":"Vector Displacement（矢量置换）输入。矢量置换数据是一个三通道数据文件，即 XYZ。"}
{"id":"7486f06f6dcdc8c71187eabfbdb30e4600fb8e1e6b3a59f01b24aed02c11494b","item_id":"092e9e8256:16","text":"还有一些用于置换的实用图案节点："}
{"id":"03463cc36381ec2fca4c74872b2869a5bbfb08ee6b922dd350acb91fd60ad68f","item_id":"092e9e8256:17","text":"对于与置换变换相关的功能，请使用"}
{"id":"e3c4a37241b9af7c66d1872d2f1f932e592a37f40a95aa243e41621696c055d7","item_id":"092e9e8256:19","text":"图案节点。"}
{"id":"cfb395b04737b78c5dddf2560579063ac49d034efa9610e136e4ee2f3adba172","item_id":"092e9e8256:20","text":"对于置换分层，请使用"}
{"id":"e3c4a37241b9af7c66d1872d2f1f932e592a37f40a95aa243e41621696c055d7","item_id":"092e9e8256:24","text":"图案节点。"}
{"id":"dbc9d1d10ce72f064a15fbca2c42d60805ff847a9edec73de28eb6aaead4e5ac","item_id":"092e9e8256:25","text":"避免多边形网格出现裂缝"}
{"id":"ad7da14e3c74a061400663dc7a914da5ef011e51584107d3c3575a7f7d504da3","item_id":"092e9e8256:26","text":"对具有硬法线的网格进行置换时，面可能会分离并产生裂缝。置换会沿顶点自身法线的方向移动顶点，但硬边两侧的相邻顶点具有不同法线，因此会朝不同方向移动，从而产生间隙或裂缝。"}
{"id":"86c1133069cff9f5a2cc156a0a29825acc4a949d4475bdcd34b926ffe4689c55","item_id":"092e9e8256:27","text":"RenderMan 提供了 \""}
{"id":"5d458104a07c301480db2ee93c79649e6899d076f2c1ab0cfcc78008a4e90c1f","item_id":"092e9e8256:28","text":"\" 属性，它会创建一份完全平滑的法线副本，并用它代替原始法线。"}
{"id":"3e141a07d401b3c074d6c91c429e83c6a2da861982f91bcdcf0647592884d158","item_id":"092e9e8256:29","text":"在 RenderMan for Blender 中，可以通过对象数据属性里的 \"Prevent polygon cracking\"（防止多边形开裂）复选框启用该属性"}
{"id":"06bcea41bc6e916d82fbedac99e9fd7de3859f946d471c5b2ed69bd3e7f27c55","item_id":"092e9e8256:30","text":"，该复选框位于网格上。"}
{"id":"d37c043e52d57d07bf38306fcd90ad8c8976d73555149afa07b857ef42b28686","item_id":"092e9e8256:31","text":"下面是为立方体网格附加置换前后的效果对比。"}
{"id":"e5d6c5241e031b2d5ac289324f405138d00f2cfed6494491d26afd3d967c3cd5","item_id":"092e9e8256:32","text":"\"Prevent polygon cracking\"（防止多边形开裂）只应在必要时启用，因为它会多占用一点内存。占用量与网格中的顶点数量成正比。"}
{"id": "bb853680249ae0d0b2608016760e0147668a6db1229576b8b27fa4d5142d609f", "item_id": "092e9e8256:2", "text": "节点。"}
{"id": "4e125a3ef68a00b029459c9aa8aa94aa07e74cc54188ffef7f60f38f016e61ca", "item_id": "092e9e8256:7", "text": "Gain"}
{"id": "e7ac0786668e0ff0f02b62bd04f45ff636fd82db63b1104601c975dc005f3a67", "item_id": "092e9e8256:8", "text": "："}
{"id": "ddf9afdd443e2577dd48cedfa6b905a1cb7c215b7e3d85564f6f71a7a8484be4", "item_id": "092e9e8256:10", "text": "Scalar Displacement"}
{"id": "b84c3fc76a6d996fe5573a9b78d2502728998886dc853d641cc50b65d37629ab", "item_id": "092e9e8256:13", "text": "Vector Displacement"}
{"id": "85d3f5d45df9c9dcfddceb0c407ec06186cc4f4c76c032986a9b2c12a0705d4a", "item_id": "092e9e8256:18", "text": "PxrDispTransform"}
{"id": "ecc4098587d3f352c2205d6b4e2590c250609dadf291b7e4eb59ebca3a8fa2f5", "item_id": "092e9e8256:21", "text": "PxrDispScalarLayer"}
{"id": "6201111b83a0cb5b0922cb37cc442b9a40e24e3b1ce100a4bb204f4c63fd2ac0", "item_id": "092e9e8256:22", "text": "和"}
{"id": "488ca18ef60afb3006b759adcf17f7c3ad467e19d618b333e69aa63c5c4ab7f3", "item_id": "092e9e8256:23", "text": "PxrDispVectorLayer"}
